Suspected kidnap kingpin Chukwudumeme Onwuamadike (Evans) was all smiles in court on Wednesday to answer to charges of kidnapping. Evans was all smile even as his gang members wear gloomy and apprehensive looks. The only female member of the gang was in pensive mood and sometimes shield her face from the flashes of camera. Evans pleaded guilty to the two count charge brought against him by the prosecution, but his lawyers said he did that under duress. 